meta {
  name: Get Payment Status
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/{{paymentId}}
  auth: bearer
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{token}}
}

docs {
  # Get Payment Status

  Queries the current status of a payment. Account numbers are masked in the response (`****4300`).

  **Statuses:** SUBMITTED → FRAUD_CHECK_IN_PROGRESS → FRAUD_APPROVED → PROCESSING_BY_BANK → COMPLETED/FAILED

  Run this after submitting a payment and waiting 3-5 seconds for async processing.
}

